last_episode_to_air.name: Reversals and Comebacks
last_episode_to_air.overview: The end is near, but to distract themselves from the catastrophe they're in, the comedians share funny stories. Finally, the Last One Standing is named!

name: Last One Standing
overview: They're comedians starring in a thrilling drama, but if their jokes don't land in the unscripted scenes, they're off the show. Let the mayhem begin!

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Lights, camera, action! The hit comedy competition wrapped in a scripted drama returns. Who will survive to earn the title of Last One Standing?

episodes.name: Light and Darkness
episodes.overview: After an action-packed opening, the first unscripted scene unfolds. The comedians try to out-funny each other by sharing some painful experiences.

episodes.name: Life and Death
episodes.overview: As a kaiju stalks the halls of the hospital, the comedians swallow some honesty-inducing pills and start dropping some hilarious truth bombs.

episodes.name: Crime and Punishment
episodes.overview: While trying to figure out who could be spreading the virus, the comedians slip into the next unscripted scene, sharing small realizations they've had.

episodes.name: Reunion and Restart
episodes.overview: In a hardboiled twist, a group of masked outlaws gathered in a hideout start sharing their painful — and comical — past experiences.

episodes.name: Falling and Flying
episodes.overview: Now in an underground fight club, a fresh crop of young comics — and, for some reason, Watabe of comedy duo Unjash — reveal their majorly laughable screwups.

episodes.name: Reality and Truth
episodes.overview: With super spy Ahn Mika captured, the comics get her to read out complaints and other negative comments she normally would never say.

episodes.name: Daigo and Daigo
episodes.overview: A woman introduces herself as Kayoko Okubo, the famous comedian, and reveals a cloning program that the gathered members may have all fallen victim to.
